{"tid":922183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赴日選AV男優奪冠　東尼大木台灣徒弟上吊亡","createTime":"2018-11-30T07:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T10:50:54.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a77177b7056af0cefe2ddc781069a1b9113d80d8","tid":922183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"桃園一名李姓男子（34歲），2015年前曾到日本參加AV男優東尼大木舉辦的選拔賽，打敗5名入選者奪冠，當時他在PPT上PO出過程，被鄉民譽為「台灣之光」、「魯蛇之光」。沒想到他昨晨被家人發現在桃園一所國小校園內上吊身亡，友人紛紛到他的臉書留言致哀。但警方對於李男的身份不願證實。 警方調查，李男前天向家人表示要外出運動，但徹夜未歸，家人透過電信公司定位，發現他出現在蘆竹區，家人趕往在一所學校附近發現他的腳踏車，但找了許久都沒發現，事後在附近一所小學校園後方遊樂器材上，發現李男上吊，家屬趕緊將他救下，李男仍不治身亡。家屬向警方表示，李男精神狀況不穩，警方初步研判，沒有外力介入，疑似憂鬱症導致輕生。3年前，李男參加東尼大木為台日友好舉辦的台灣AV男優選拔，李男打敗5名同時入選者奪冠，獲得一萬日圓獎金及與AV女優較勁機會。李男事後接受《蘋果》訪問時曾指出，靠朋友及雙胞胎哥哥贊助七千元，才有錢買單程廉航機票，拍攝過程，李男說不緊張、也不怕鏡頭。李男輕生消息今天傳出後，不少好友都留言哀傷。朋友紛紛留言「 祝福你不再被精神問題折磨，在另一個世界再當個瀟灑帥氣的劍士吧」、「辛苦你了 R.I.P.」。（突發中心石明啟／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_b4f9217844c71815f23e744ad256f35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_b4f9217844c71815f23e744ad256f35a.jpg&h=896390a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李姓男子昨晨上吊身亡。翻攝李姓男子臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_b691860d2904f2dd5a6e9d5774c4c359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_b691860d2904f2dd5a6e9d5774c4c359.jpg&h=08823ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n友人在李男臉書上致哀。翻攝李姓男子臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_216cb38d138ae64a334ab4c321b62621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_216cb38d138ae64a334ab4c321b62621.jpg&h=f49723e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東尼大木（中）當時與六名參賽者在拍攝期間，一起吃高級便當。資料照片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_9cd810b0a3b07edcce99ec67b595c00c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_9cd810b0a3b07edcce99ec67b595c00c.jpg&h=2a1b60b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李男3年前曾接受《蘋果》專訪談參選AV男優心情。資料照片"},{"pid":"a621d6c134f4c0e8a4eb1eaffa4ca9504cab0345","tid":922183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_8150a2f20329e4fe393d655ad8d65c4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_8150a2f20329e4fe393d655ad8d65c4a.jpg&h=0f01901d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李男臉書PO著他與AV女優照片。翻攝李姓男子臉書"},{"pid":"be4c0e201552d9fa2474215876c150c93bb5a17a","tid":922183,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a621d6c134f4c0e8a4eb1eaffa4ca9504cab0345","tid":922183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181130/640_8150a2f20329e4fe393d655ad8d65c4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181130%2F640_8150a2f20329e4fe393d655ad8d65c4a.jpg&h=0f01901d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李男臉書PO著他與AV女優照片。翻攝李姓男子臉書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"里美？"},{"pid":"13c77b5c6fbfbb95d1e8bcd34a40f1c254eb52a1","tid":922183,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:28:34.000Z","msg":"周董?"},{"pid":"9f07c387fa1b0f11787f697323c635c44121752a","tid":922183,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛！！記得佢幾靚仔，個陣仲要有巴打求seed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets